Package br.com.concepting.framework.ui.components

Class BaseComponent

java.lang.Object
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport
br.com.concepting.framework.ui.components.BaseComponent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActionFormComponent, BaseActionFormComponent, ClockComponent, OptionStateComponent, PageComponent, ScriptComponent, StyleComponent, SystemComponent
public abstract class BaseComponent extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport implements Cloneable
Class that defines the basic implementation of a component.
